├── collection.json ← Collection page │ ├── cart.json ← Cart page │ ├── page.json ← Generic page │ ├── blog.json ← Blog listing │ ├── article.json ← Single blog post │ ├── search.json ← Search results │ ├── 404.json ← Error page │ ├── customers/ │ │ ├── login.json ← Login page │ │ ├── register.json ← Register page │ │ └── account.json ← Account page │ └── *.liquid ← Purane liquid templates (legacy) │ ├── 📁 sections/ │ ├── header.liquid ← Website ka header │ ├── footer.liquid ← Website ka footer │ ├── announcement-bar.liquid │ ├── hero-banner.liquid │ ├── featured-collection.liquid │ └── [tumhari custom sections] │ ├── 📁 snippets/ │ ├── product-card.liquid ← Reusable product card │ ├── price.liquid ← Price display logic │ ├── icon-arrow.liquid ← SVG icons │ └── [chote reusable pieces] │ ├── 📁 assets/ │ ├── base.css ← Main stylesheet │ ├── theme.js ← Main JavaScript │ ├── component-*.css ← Component styles │ └── section-*.js ← Section scripts │ ├── 📁 config/ │ ├── settings_schema.json ← Theme Settings ka schema (structure) │ └── settings_data.json ← Theme Settings ki saved values │ ├── 📁 locales/ │ ├── en.default.json ← English translations │ └── [other languages] │ └── 📁 blocks/ (new — Shopify 2.0+) └── [reusable block types] ``` --- ### LESSON 3 — File Connections Ka Map ``` BROWSER REQUEST AAYA ↓ layout/theme.liquid ← HAR PAGE IS SE GUZARTA HAI ↓ ├── {{ content_for_header }} ← CSS, JS, meta tags └── {{ content_for_layout }} ← Page ka actual content ↓ templates/[page].json ← Konsa page hai? ↓ sections/[section].liquid ← Sections render hoti hain ↓ snippets/[snippet].liquid ← Chote pieces render hote hain ↓ assets/ (CSS + JS) ← Style aur behavior load hoti hai ↓ config/settings_data.json ← Merchant ki settings apply hoti hain ``` --- ### LESSON 4 — Ek File Kitni Doosri Files Se Judi Hai? #### layout/theme.liquid connections: ``` theme.liquid ├── LOADS → assets/base.css ├── LOADS → assets/theme.js ├── RENDERS → sections/announcement-bar.liquid ├── RENDERS → sections/header.liquid ├── RENDERS → {{ content_for_layout }} → templates/*.json ├── RENDERS → sections/footer.liquid └── READS → config/settings_data.json (colors, fonts, etc.) Connections: 10-20+ files ``` #### sections/header.liquid connections: ``` header.liquid ├── READS → config/settings_data.json (logo, colors) ├── READS → shop.navigation (menu links) ├── RENDERS → snippets/icon-search.liquid ├── RENDERS → snippets/icon-cart.liquid ├── RENDERS → snippets/icon-account.liquid ├── LOADS → assets/section-header.css └── LOADS → assets/section-header.js Connections: 7-10 files ``` #### templates/product.json connections: ``` product.json ├── CALLS → sections/main-product.liquid │ ├── RENDERS → snippets/product-media.liquid │ ├── RENDERS → snippets/price.liquid │ ├── RENDERS → snippets/product-variant-picker.liquid │ ├── RENDERS → snippets/buy-buttons.liquid │ └── READS → product object (Shopify data) └── CALLS → sections/related-products.liquid └── RENDERS → snippets/product-card.liquid Connections: 8-15 files ``` --- ### LESSON 5 — Har File Ka Role (Simple Words Mein) | File Type | Role | Misaal | |-----------|------|--------| | `layout/*.liquid` | Ghar ka dhanca | Walls, roof, foundation | | `templates/*.json` | Kamre ka plan | Living room ka layout | | `sections/*.liquid` | Kamre ka saman | Sofa, TV, table | | `snippets/*.liquid` | Chhoti cheezein | Cushion, remote, cup | | `assets/*.css` | Rang aur design | Paint, wallpaper | | `assets/*.js` | Bijli ka kaam | Switches, fans, AC | | `config/settings_schema.json` | Settings ka menu | Customizer options | | `config/settings_data.json` | Saved choices | Jo merchant ne choose kiya | | `locales/*.json` | Translation book | Different languages | --- ### LESSON 6 — Theme Files Ko Samajhne Ka Fayda #### Tum yeh kar sakte ho: **1. CUSTOM SECTIONS BANANA** ``` Tumhari apni custom section banana Jo sirf tumhare store ke liye ho Jo merchant customize kar sake ``` **2. EXISTING SECTIONS MODIFY KARNA** ``` Dawn theme ka header modify karna Footer mein naya column add karna Product page pe custom fields add karna ``` **3. SNIPPETS BANANA** ``` Reusable product card banana Rating stars component banana Custom badge system banana ``` **4. THEME SETTINGS ADD KARNA** ``` settings_schema.json mein naye options Merchant ko zyada control dena Brand colors, fonts globally set karna ``` **5. FULL CUSTOM THEME BANANA** ``` Scratch se apna premium theme Apna khud ka template system Complete custom design system ``` **6. THEME OPTIMIZATION** ``` Page speed improve karna Lazy loading add karna Critical CSS separate karna ``` --- ### LESSON 7 — Connection Logic — IF YEH KARO TU KYA HOGA #### SCENARIO 1: theme.liquid mein change karo ``` IF: theme.liquid mein kuch change kiya THEN: Har page pe change dikhai dega WHY: Kyunki har page theme.liquid se guzarta hai Example: theme.liquid mein font load kiya Result: Poori website pe font change ho gaya ``` #### SCENARIO 2: Section file delete karo ``` IF: sections/header.liquid delete kiya THEN: Har page pe header missing ho jayega WHY: theme.liquid header section ko call karta hai Error: "Could not find asset sections/header.liquid" ``` #### SCENARIO 3: settings_schema.json mein galti ``` IF: settings_schema.json mein range step galat THEN: Theme customizer mein error aayega WHY: Shopify schema validate karta hai load pe Error: "Setting 'bar_height' must be a step in the range" ``` #### SCENARIO 4: Snippet rename karo ``` IF: snippets/price.liquid ko snippets/my-price.liquid kiya THEN: Har jagah price nahi dikhega jahan render tha WHY: {% render 'price' %} → file dhundhti hai 'price' naam se Error: "Could not find asset snippets/price.liquid" ``` #### SCENARIO 5: assets mein JS add karo ``` IF: assets/my-feature.js banaya but load nahi kiya THEN: Feature kaam nahi karega WHY: File exist karti hai but koi load nahi kar raha Fix: Section ya theme.liquid mein script tag add karo ``` --- ### LESSON 8 — Dawn Theme Ka Specific System Dawn theme Shopify 2.0 pe based hai: ``` Dawn Theme Special Features: │ ├── JSON Templates (nahin purane .liquid templates) │ Merchant sections ko drag & drop kar sakta hai │ ├── Section Groups │ Header aur Footer pe bhi sections hoti hain │ ├── Color Schemes │ 5 color schemes — ek jagah set, sab jagah apply │ ├── CSS Custom Properties │ --color-background, --color-foreground │ Sab variables se theme ka color system chalta hai │ ├── Web Components │ <product-form>, <cart-notification> │ Custom HTML elements JavaScript se powered │ └── Deferred Loading Images, scripts lazy load hote hain Page speed optimize rehti hai ``` --- ### LESSON 9 — Ek File Banana Ka Complete Process ``` STEP 1: Plan karo Kya banana hai? Kya features chahiye? STEP 2: File banao sections/my-section.liquid STEP 3: Liquid HTML likho {% for block in section.blocks %}...{% endfor %} STEP 4: CSS likho (scoped) #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} { ... } STEP 5: JavaScript likho (IIFE) (function(){ ... })(); STEP 6: Schema likho {% schema %}{ ... }{% endschema %} STEP 7: Template mein add karo templates/index.json mein section reference STEP 8: Test karo Customizer mein dekho — settings kaam karti hain? STEP 9: Mobile check karo Responsive hai? STEP 10: Publish karo Theme publish — live ho gaya! ``` --- ### LESSON 10 — Common Mistakes Aur Unka Logic ``` MISTAKE 1: Same ID do sections mein PROBLEM: Shopify confuse ho jata hai FIX: Har section ke IDs mein unique prefix lagao MISTAKE 2: External CSS file jo exist nahi PROBLEM: 404 error — style load nahi hoti FIX: CSS section file mein hi likho MISTAKE 3: JavaScript global scope mein PROBLEM: Doosre sections ke JS se conflict FIX: Hamesha IIFE use karo MISTAKE 4: Range step galat PROBLEM: Customizer error — setting save nahi hoti FIX: (max-min)/step <= 100 formula check karo MISTAKE 5: block.shopify_attributes missing PROBLEM: Editor mein block highlight nahi hota FIX: Har block div pe {{ block.shopify_attributes }} MISTAKE 6: Snippet naam galat PROBLEM: Render error — page crash FIX: {% render 'exact-file-name' %} — extension nahi ``` --- ## 🧪 MENTOR SE SEEKHNE KA TARIKA ### Jab koi naya topic puchho: ``` Tum yeh format use karo: "Mentor, mujhe [TOPIC] samjhao: - Main abhi [CURRENT LEVEL] pe hoon - Mujhe [SPECIFIC CHEEZ] samajhni hai - Mera goal hai [GOAL] - Example chahiye: [HAN/NAHI]" ``` ### Mentor ka jawab hamesha hoga: ``` 1. Simple explanation (1 paragraph) 2. Real example (code ya analogy) 3. Connection diagram (kaun si file kisse judi) 4. Agar yeh karo toh kya hoga (IF-THEN logic) 5. Common mistakes is topic mein 6. Practice task 7. "Kya samajh aaya? Koi sawaal?" ``` --- ## 💬 MENTOR SE PUCHH SAKTE HO Yeh sawaal puchho jab chaaho: ``` BEGINNER SAWAAL: "Yeh file kya karti hai?" "Yeh error kyun aa raha hai?" "Dono mein farq kya hai?" INTERMEDIATE SAWAAL: "Yeh feature kaise banao?" "Is approach ka kya fayda/nuqsan hai?" "Performance ke liye kya better hai?" ADVANCED SAWAAL: "Yeh architecture kyun aise design ki?" "Is pattern ka alternative kya hai?" "Scale karne pe kya problems aayengi?" ``` --- ## 🎯 AAJ KA SAWAAL FORMAT Jab bhi kuch puchho: ``` TOPIC: [Kya samajhna hai] LEVEL: [Beginner / Intermediate / Advanced] CONTEXT: [Kya kar rahe ho abhi] CONFUSION: [Exactly kya samajh nahi aaya]
 
 
