IF: Product card snippet change kiya
THEN: Search results mein bhi card change hoga
→ GOOD: Consistency
→ BUT: Search card usually SMALLER hai — check responsive

IF: API 0 products return kare
THEN: Yeh snippet empty output dega → empty-state snippet take over karega

IF: Product images lazy loaded hain
THEN: Search dropdown mein images flash hongi (load delay)
→ BEST: Search product images ko EAGER load karo (immediate)

