IMPORTANT CONCEPT — Metafields:

METAFIELDS = Extra data stored on Shopify objects (products, collections, etc.)

Standard Shopify product data:
→ title, description, price, images, variants (BUILT-IN)

Metafields (CUSTOM data):
→ reviews.rating = 4.5
→ custom.material = "Genuine Leather"
→ custom.care_instructions = "Wipe with damp cloth"
→ shipping.weight_kg = 0.5

Apps use metafields to STORE their data.
Theme blocks use metafields to READ and DISPLAY that data.


